data.description: Check out this charming home sitting on 7.3 Acres, Close to town but still secluded for privacy! Your gorgeous and grand front porch enters you into your adorable and trendy entry way! Cozy living room with a whitewashed brick fireplace and bookshelf! A kitchen loaded with character, featuring a whitewashed brick accent wall equipped with your built in Cooktop, and wall-oven! Spacious 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, and a bonus room that could be an office, sitting room, or 4th bedroom, the possibilities are endless! Large covered back patio, perfect for entertaining in your massive back yard that is loaded with BEAUTIFUL live oaks! A huge carport and laundry room! Metal roof is only 3 years old, and HVAC and deep well were replaced 6 years ago! You DO NOT want to miss out on this gem of a home!
